{"tid":2347772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英檔解密：遊行須警批准 社團禁通外國  董搞「國安」惡法與英鬧翻","createTime":"2020-12-31T09:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:47:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43edf0ac7db5c1e98e91c84d37ce10d309b2932a","tid":2347772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/OB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FOB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=914225fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FOB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU%2F&h=3e71e5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/OB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英檔解密：遊行須警批准 社團禁通外國 <br />\n董搞「國安」惡法與英鬧翻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NKL7CAqNZagCwMYNujxlLxF0iIM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTWSSVNXABH2PPGIWVXXXW7FWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNKL7CAqNZagCwMYNujxlLxF0iIM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJTWSSVNXABH2PPGIWVXXXW7FWM.jpg&h=f617662f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港主權移交前，董建華（左）與時任港督彭定康（右）曾會面討論《公安條例》及《社團條例》，最終不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n任內力推23條的前特首、<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發財事大 歐多國放軟監察人權<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席董建華今年多次為港版國安法護航。<br />\n<br />\n國最新一批解密檔案顯示，早在主權移交前，<br />\n<br />\n時為候任特首的董建華已表明希望還原《公安條例》及《社團條例》，<br />\n<br />\n惟英方對此有保留。<br />\n<br />\n董其後即以雙方意見分歧為由，拒絕出席青嶼幹線開幕儀式。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰關玉婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pmkSSLNoA-OOHgNjH82aDwqaMok=/2247x785/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MRMLBPTDXJFUPLZXIXEFSLYYEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpmkSSLNoA-OOHgNjH82aDwqaMok%3D%2F2247x785%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMRMLBPTDXJFUPLZXIXEFSLYYEY.jpg&h=53b24452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■最新解封的英國檔案披露一份1997年4月的文件，董建華向時任港督彭定康表示需要修訂《社團條例》及《公安條例》，稱需要堅決維持公眾秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T_nVtqWHdALexSS9LZ7_K-E0AN8=/2399x661/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UPEZVNWCOBB3XBTIP3G3CVFFTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT_nVtqWHdALexSS9LZ7_K-E0AN8%3D%2F2399x661%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUPEZVNWCOBB3XBTIP3G3CVFFTM.jpg&h=87903f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■董促彭定康與臨立會合作，「接受現實」。<br />\n<br />\n港英政府分別於1992及1995年因應《人權法案條例》放寬《社團條例》及《公安條例》，以通知制度取代註冊社團及申請遊行制度，惟其後被人大常委指牴觸《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭定康促諮詢公眾<br />\n<br />\n最新解封的英國檔案包括一份1997年4月的文件，披露董建華與時任港督彭定康會面內容。董在會上向彭定康表示，需要修訂《社團條例》及《公安條例》，尤其強調政黨不應接受來自外國資助。彭定康回應稱，按董論調，若有中國或香港名人反過來被發現向美國政黨提供資助，即會為董帶來政治麻煩。但董沒有理會，只稱需要堅決維持公眾秩序。彭定康認為香港已是一個穩定、守法的社會，犯罪率持續下降，要求董就修訂進行公眾諮詢，會面最終不歡而散。文件中提及董建華其後以「不想成為鎂光燈的焦點」及雙方意見分歧為由，拒絕出席該月底舉行的青嶼幹線開幕儀式。<br />\n<br />\n1996年底，中方一意孤行。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jUVEGe22w1yqq2gnM4V4F__Dmxk=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VB6W6TVFSZD6LIE6SVZ56J2SIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjUVEGe22w1yqq2gnM4V4F__Dmxk%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVB6W6TVFSZD6LIE6SVZ56J2SIM.jpg&h=2380ad72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■回歸後警方屢被轟選擇性執法，觸發連串示威，要求修訂《公安條例》之聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關心禮賓府風水<br />\n<br />\n文件字裏行間不乏英方官員對董建華的不滿。如兩人在另一次私下會面中，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n1997年6月，在深圳開會的臨立會通過還原惡法，重新收緊《公安條例》及《社團條例》。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹指，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"601ae2aebc90ffaffa7f430f5f09d837474423d1","tid":2347772,"uid":284432,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"affa6709b47508228c6583f47479fdd68e7c5ce2","tid":2347772,"uid":357710,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43edf0ac7db5c1e98e91c84d37ce10d309b2932a","tid":2347772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/OB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FOB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=914225fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FOB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU%2F&h=3e71e5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/OB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英檔解密：遊行須警批准 社團禁通外國 <br />\n董搞「國安」惡法與英鬧翻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NKL7CAqNZagCwMYNujxlLxF0iIM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTWSSVNXABH2PPGIWVXXXW7FWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNKL7CAqNZagCwMYNujxlLxF0iIM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJTWSSVNXABH2PPGIWVXXXW7FWM.jpg&h=f617662f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港主權移交前，董建華（左）與時任港督彭定康（右）曾會面討論《公安條例》及《社團條例》，最終不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n任內力推23條的前特首、<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發財事大 歐多國放軟監察人權<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席董建華今年多次為港版國安法護航。<br />\n<br />\n國最新一批解密檔案顯示，早在主權移交前，<br />\n<br />\n時為候任特首的董建華已表明希望還原《公安條例》及《社團條例》，<br />\n<br />\n惟英方對此有保留。<br />\n<br />\n董其後即以雙方意見分歧為由，拒絕出席青嶼幹線開幕儀式。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰關玉婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pmkSSLNoA-OOHgNjH82aDwqaMok=/2247x785/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MRMLBPTDXJFUPLZXIXEFSLYYEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpmkSSLNoA-OOHgNjH82aDwqaMok%3D%2F2247x785%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMRMLBPTDXJFUPLZXIXEFSLYYEY.jpg&h=53b24452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■最新解封的英國檔案披露一份1997年4月的文件，董建華向時任港督彭定康表示需要修訂《社團條例》及《公安條例》，稱需要堅決維持公眾秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T_nVtqWHdALexSS9LZ7_K-E0AN8=/2399x661/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UPEZVNWCOBB3XBTIP3G3CVFFTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT_nVtqWHdALexSS9LZ7_K-E0AN8%3D%2F2399x661%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUPEZVNWCOBB3XBTIP3G3CVFFTM.jpg&h=87903f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■董促彭定康與臨立會合作，「接受現實」。<br />\n<br />\n港英政府分別於1992及1995年因應《人權法案條例》放寬《社團條例》及《公安條例》，以通知制度取代註冊社團及申請遊行制度，惟其後被人大常委指牴觸《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭定康促諮詢公眾<br />\n<br />\n最新解封的英國檔案包括一份1997年4月的文件，披露董建華與時任港督彭定康會面內容。董在會上向彭定康表示，需要修訂《社團條例》及《公安條例》，尤其強調政黨不應接受來自外國資助。彭定康回應稱，按董論調，若有中國或香港名人反過來被發現向美國政黨提供資助，即會為董帶來政治麻煩。但董沒有理會，只稱需要堅決維持公眾秩序。彭定康認為香港已是一個穩定、守法的社會，犯罪率持續下降，要求董就修訂進行公眾諮詢，會面最終不歡而散。文件中提及董建華其後以「不想成為鎂光燈的焦點」及雙方意見分歧為由，拒絕出席該月底舉行的青嶼幹線開幕儀式。<br />\n<br />\n1996年底，中方一意孤行。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jUVEGe22w1yqq2gnM4V4F__Dmxk=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VB6W6TVFSZD6LIE6SVZ56J2SIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjUVEGe22w1yqq2gnM4V4F__Dmxk%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVB6W6TVFSZD6LIE6SVZ56J2SIM.jpg&h=2380ad72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■回歸後警方屢被轟選擇性執法，觸發連串示威，要求修訂《公安條例》之聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關心禮賓府風水<br />\n<br />\n文件字裏行間不乏英方官員對董建華的不滿。如兩人在另一次私下會面中，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n1997年6月，在深圳開會的臨立會通過還原惡法，重新收緊《公安條例》及《社團條例》。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹指，。。。。。。。。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"即是光復1992年港英法例"},{"pid":"18d17a0f98fb08c4d6c2ef6ea65d2b9634d7a49c","tid":2347772,"uid":4964,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"601ae2aebc90ffaffa7f430f5f09d837474423d1","tid":2347772,"uid":284432,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"明顯係中共寫基本法個陣已經諗好"},{"pid":"99d1f5c5fad27bf98bae3c6ad2fee22092be0bac","tid":2347772,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f470ceb62419142f69744bb326802a7afa676d88","tid":2347772,"uid":335434,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"601ae2aebc90ffaffa7f430f5f09d837474423d1","tid":2347772,"uid":284432,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"黑心嚟講老懵董不下於689同林奠 <br />\n只係佢個人本身好撚廢執行能力又低 所以佢任內先「一事無成」姐 只有果啲唔撚知情嘅港豬先會吹奏佢都算係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52729037c7b915f4b22cce306448b384d19329e9","tid":2347772,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"affa6709b47508228c6583f47479fdd68e7c5ce2","tid":2347772,"uid":357710,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43edf0ac7db5c1e98e91c84d37ce10d309b2932a","tid":2347772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/OB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FOB4USY44CJA6TBL4WMIIODU5ZU%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJ